openkms.gpj

Class AIDRegistryEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • openkms.gpj.AIDRegistryEntry

  • public class AIDRegistryEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    One entry in the card registry. Describes one entry of the card registry, consisting of
    • application ID (as AID)
    • the life cycle status (as integer)
    • the privileges (in encoded form as integer)
    • the list of ?? (as array of AID's
    • and the kind
